= Hickey

Supporting Hickey version: 0.0.x

Hickey is a DSL for preparing Rails test database.

== Installation

=== Normal Installation

You can install Hickey with the following command.

  % ruby install.rb

from its distribution directory.

=== GEM Installation

Download and install Hickey with the following.

   gem install --remote hickey

== License

Hickey is available under an Apache License Version 2.0.

== Support

Feel free to submit commits or feature requests.  If you send a patch,
remember to update the corresponding unit tests.  If fact, I prefer
new feature to be submitted in the form of new unit tests.

For other information, feel free to ask on the ruby-talk mailing list or contact
mailto:iam@li-xiao.com.

